WEBVTT

00:00:00.038 --> 00:00:01.664 align:center line:79%
Why do we still look like this?
- Huh?

00:00:01.664 --> 00:00:03.124 align:center line:81%
Wow!

00:00:03.124 --> 00:00:04.167 align:center line:81%
Much better!

00:00:11.507 --> 00:00:13.051 align:center line:81%
What is the meaning of life?

00:00:13.176 --> 00:00:15.845 align:center line:81%
Is there a God or a spiritual dimension?

00:00:16.054 --> 00:00:18.139 align:center line:81%
I tried so many different identities.

00:00:18.139 --> 00:00:20.099 align:center line:81%
I wasn’t really sure exactly who I should be.

00:00:20.433 --> 00:00:21.726 align:center line:81%
What am I putting my hope in?

00:00:21.726 --> 00:00:23.186 align:center line:81%
What can I do to change the world?

00:00:23.186 --> 00:00:24.562 align:center line:81%
That little feeling of love,

00:00:24.562 --> 00:00:25.897 align:center line:81%
it changed my life forever.

00:00:25.897 --> 00:00:27.607 align:center line:81%
[What’s on your mind?]

00:00:30.902 --> 00:00:33.112 align:center line:81%
Welcome to the conversation.

00:00:33.821 --> 00:00:34.989 align:center line:81%
Hello, everyone.

00:00:34.989 --> 00:00:36.115 align:center line:81%
Let’s go.

00:00:36.115 --> 00:00:38.159 align:center line:81%
Wow!

00:00:40.119 --> 00:00:41.245 align:center line:81%
See you, Isaac.

00:00:42.705 --> 00:00:44.665 align:center line:81%
We are on the Sea of Galilee.

00:00:44.665 --> 00:00:46.626 align:center line:81%
Really freak out!

00:00:46.626 --> 00:00:48.377 align:center line:81%
Aah!

00:00:48.711 --> 00:00:50.254 align:center line:81%
Engaging landing gear.

00:00:51.756 --> 00:00:52.882 align:center line:81%
My avatar looks good.

00:00:55.635 --> 00:00:57.095 align:center line:81%
Guys, I had to try.

00:00:59.055 --> 00:01:01.057 align:center line:81%
Alpha was created to be a space to listen, 

00:01:01.057 --> 00:01:02.934 align:center line:81%
ask questions, and explore the deeper

00:01:02.934 --> 00:01:04.769 align:center line:81%
questions of life and faith.

00:01:05.895 --> 00:01:07.730 align:center line:81%
Alpha is a space where you can share

00:01:07.730 --> 00:01:09.565 align:center line:81%
what you think and how you feel.

00:01:09.565 --> 00:01:10.858 align:center line:81%
I believed I could do anything

00:01:10.858 --> 00:01:11.943 align:center line:81%
I set my mind to.

00:01:11.943 --> 00:01:13.486 align:center line:81%
This is your space.

00:01:14.237 --> 00:01:15.446 align:center line:81%
Everybody wants to be happy.

00:01:15.446 --> 00:01:16.447 align:center line:81%
What makes you happy?

00:01:16.447 --> 00:01:17.907 align:center line:81%
Pizza.

00:01:17.907 --> 00:01:19.033 align:center line:81%
Dogs and cats.

00:01:24.789 --> 00:01:27.166 align:center line:81%
Your journey is just getting started.
